description._content: SDASM.TITLE: Ecuador I Airplane SDASM.CATALOG: Gildred_00149 SDASM.DATE: 22-Jul-32 SDASM.LOCATION: Cuenca, Ecuador SDASM.ADDITIONAL INFORMATION: Avion ""Ecuador"" Aereodromo ""Mariscal Irama."" Raid Latacunga - Cunca efectuado por los aviadores nacionales Cptnes Luis A. Mantilla, Cosme Rennella y Bruno Cecoville (mecamico) el 22 de Julio de 1932 a las 9,54 a.m. - Cunca - Ecuador. ""Ecuador"" Plane at airfield ""Mariscal Lamar."" Endurance run from Latacunga - Cuenca being done by Ecuadorian pilots Captains Luis A. Mantilla, Cosme Rennellay, Bruno Cecoville (mechanic), the 22nd of July, 1932, at 9:54 AM at Cuenca Ecuador.
